Dollar Tree Coupon Matchups ~ Week of 2/13/15 Dollar Tree Shopping Tips:


Dollar Tree only accepts manufacturers coupons. They do not accept any store coupons.
Only two (2) print-at-home Internet Coupons may be used per household per day.
Only four (4) Identical Manufactuer Coupons may be used per household per day.
Coupons for FREE items are only accepted if a purchase is required to get one free (i.e. B1G1 coupons).
Watch the SIZE of the item compared to the limitation on the coupon (sometimes they dont match).
Coupons cannot be redeemed for more than the purchase price of the item (no overage).
Only one (1) manufacturers coupon will be accepted per item.
Sometimes it is good to print the Coupon Policy HERE and bring it with you in case the cashier has a concern.
Be sure to read our guide for Using Coupons at Dollar Tree before you go!

Garnier hat sich dem Trend angeschlossen und bereits letztes Jahr einige Mizellenwasser auf den Markt gebracht.
